trans-unit.source: A class that wraps a specified writer and delegates all <xref:System.Xml.XmlDictionaryWriter> calls to the wrapped writer.
trans-unit.target: Egy osztály, amely egy megadott írói becsomagolja, és delegálja összes <xref:System.Xml.XmlDictionaryWriter>a becsomagolt író hívásainak.</xref:System.Xml.XmlDictionaryWriter>

trans-unit.source: The writer that is wrapped can be accessed through the <xref:System.IdentityModel.DelegatingXmlDictionaryWriter.InnerWriter%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Az író be van burkolva is elérhetőek a <xref:System.IdentityModel.DelegatingXmlDictionaryWriter.InnerWriter%2A>tulajdonság.</xref:System.IdentityModel.DelegatingXmlDictionaryWriter.InnerWriter%2A>

trans-unit.source: Call the <xref:System.IdentityModel.DelegatingXmlDictionaryWriter.InitializeInnerWriter%2A> method to set the wrapped writer and initialize the property.
trans-unit.target: Hívja a <xref:System.IdentityModel.DelegatingXmlDictionaryWriter.InitializeInnerWriter%2A>metódus a becsomagolt író és a tulajdonság inicializálása.</xref:System.IdentityModel.DelegatingXmlDictionaryWriter.InitializeInnerWriter%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can call the <xref:System.IdentityModel.DelegatingXmlDictionaryWriter.InitializeTracingWriter%2A> method to set an <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> to which non-canonical XML will be echoed.
trans-unit.target: Hívása a <xref:System.IdentityModel.DelegatingXmlDictionaryWriter.InitializeTracingWriter%2A>módszer beállítása az <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>melyik nem kanonikus XML-fájlba fogja annál.</xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> </xref:System.IdentityModel.DelegatingXmlDictionaryWriter.InitializeTracingWriter%2A>
